OL,3,CRoots and Coming To America star John
OL,4,CAmos dies aged 84
OL,6,FJohn Amos, who starred in the seminal
OL,7,F1977 TV series Roots and appeared
OL,8,Falongside Eddie Murphy in comedy film
OL,9,FComing to America, has died at the age
OL,10,Fof 84.
OL,12,FThe US actor died on August 21 in Los
OL,13,FAngeles of natural causes, his
OL,14,Fpublicist Belinda Foster said.
OL,16,F"He was a man with the kindest heart
OL,17,Fand a heart of gold ... and he was
OL,18,Floved the world over," his son, Kelly
OL,19,FChristopher Amos, said in a statement.
