OL,6,F"Many fans consider him their TV
OL,7,Ffather. He lived a good life. His
OL,8,Flegacy will live on in his outstanding
OL,9,Fworks in television and film as an
OL,10,Factor."
OL,12,FHis agent, Julia Buchwald, added: "His
OL,13,Fimpact on the industry and those who
OL,14,Fknew him will never be forgotten."
OL,16,FAmos shot to fame in the 1970s when he
OL,17,Fplayed Gordy Howard, the weatherman on
OL,18,FThe Mary Tyler Moore Show.
