OL,6,FIt led to his role as family patriarch
OL,7,FJames Evans Sr in the Norman Lear
OL,8,Fsitcom, Good Times, which featured one
OL,9,Fof television's first black two-parent
OL,10,Ffamilies.
OL,12,FHe went on to portray the older
OL,13,Fversion of Kunta Kinte in the ground-
OL,14,Fbreaking miniseries, Roots.
OL,16,FAmos scored his only Emmy nomination
OL,17,Ffor his role in the 1977 series which
OL,18,Fdepicted the atrocities of slavery.
