OL,6,FIn 2020, Amos was inducted into the
OL,7,FNew Jersey Hall of Fame. Prior to his
OL,8,Facting career, Amos served as a member
OL,9,Fof the New Jersey State National
OL,10,FGuard, and in 2020 was inducted into
OL,11,Fthe New Jersey Hall of Fame.
OL,13,FHe is survived by daughter Shannon, a
OL,14,Fformer entertainment executive, and
OL,15,FKelly Christopher, a Grammy-nominated
OL,16,Fvideo music director and editor.
OL,18,FThey were from his first marriage to
OL,19,FNoel Mickelson, whom he met in
OL,20,Fcollege. His second marriage to actor
OL,21,FLillian Lehman also ended in divorce.
